A prompt is essentially a command or an instruction given to an AI system which it then interprets and responds to. In the context mentioned above, the prompt is the command given to the AI, ChatGPT, to write a short haiku about the importance of understanding AI for improving the world. The system responds by generating an appropriate message in line with the topic. The same prompt can elicit slightly different responses each time due to the probabilistic nature of the AI system. Despite the variety of responses, each one will be relevant to the given prompt. The system's ability to reply to prompts in different ways demonstrates its flexibility and versatility.